WEBVTT

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.336
SC: And I remember us all
being gathered around

00:03:04.360 --> 00:03:06.056
to sing that song,

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:09.576
"If you're happy and you know it,
clap your hands." You know that one?

00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:13.056
And I remember thinking,
I was happy five minutes ago,

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:15.416
when I was hanging out
with my friend over there,

00:03:15.440 --> 00:03:19.056
and I'm not happy now and I don't know
why they're making us sing this song.

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:20.336
I feel so ridiculous.

00:03:20.360 --> 00:03:22.416
AG: Susan didn't know
the word at the time,

00:03:22.440 --> 00:03:25.496
but decades later
she discovered she was an introvert.

00:03:25.520 --> 00:03:27.056
A light bulb went off.

00:03:27.080 --> 00:03:29.616
She dove headfirst into the science.

